{"total":18,"pageSize":10,"pageCount":2,"data":[{"title":"CRAZY","slug":"crazy","date":"2021-01-24T02:22:06.549Z","updated":"2021-01-24T02:24:18.252Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/crazy.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210124101828160.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=reverse&number=4&grade=1&id=5509&page=2\">CRAZY</a></p>\n<p>64位linux程序，使用ida进行静态分析发现，可以发现输入的字符串，在HighTemplar::calculate函数进行操作，然后判断是否与目标字符串相同，最后输出</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210124101828160.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>字符串进行了<code>(s^0x50+23)^0x13+11</code>的操作，得到参与判断的字符串<br>因此写出解密脚本，得到flag</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> hashlib <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> md5</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">ans = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;327a6c4304ad5938eaf0efb6cc3e53dc&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">s= <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>.join(<span class=\"built_in\">map</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>, <span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">map</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">lambda</span> x:((((<span class=\"built_in\">ord</span>(x)-<span class=\"number\">11</span>)^<span class=\"number\">0x13</span>)-<span class=\"number\">23</span>)^<span class=\"number\">0x50</span>), <span class=\"built_in\">list</span>(s)))))</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;flag&#123;&#x27;</span>+s+<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#125;&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>l</p>\n","text":"CRAZY64位linux程序，使用ida进行静态分析发现，可以发现输入的字符串，在HighTemplar::calculate函数进行操作，然后判断是否与目标字符串相同，最后输出 [Figure] l","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"RSA256","slug":"rsa256","date":"2021-01-24T02:12:09.170Z","updated":"2021-01-24T02:24:38.008Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/rsa256.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2021012410090929.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=5485&page=2\">RSA256</a></p>\n<p>得到为RSA密钥文件以及密文，利用openssl库，打开密钥文件，得到N和公钥，<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2021012410090929.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>拿到N后利用factordb，进行素因子分解可以得到p和q，进而得到了私钥<br>然后构建解密脚本得到，解密密文，得到flag</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> gmpy2</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> Crypto.PublicKey <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> RSA</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> rsa</span><br><span class=\"line\">p=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">273821108020968288372911424519201044333</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">q=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">280385007186315115828483000867559983517</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">n=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">76775333340223961139427050707840417811156978085146970312315886671546666259161</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">e=<span class=\"number\">65537</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">fai=(p-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*(q-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(p*q)</span><br><span class=\"line\">d=gmpy2.invert(e,fai)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(d)</span><br><span class=\"line\">p=<span class=\"number\">273821108020968288372911424519201044333</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">q=<span class=\"number\">280385007186315115828483000867559983517</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">fai=(p-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*(q-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">n=<span class=\"number\">76775333340223961139427050707840417811156978085146970312315886671546666259161</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">d=<span class=\"number\">49807846676324857039001173611017456460524559498389088122317223352151924725265</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">privatekey=rsa.PrivateKey(n,e,d,p,q)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##Key=privatekey.export_key()</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##with open(&#x27;prikey.pem&#x27;,&#x27;wb&#x27;) as fp:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##    fp.write(Key)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;fllllllag.txt&#x27;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&#x27;rb&#x27;</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> fp:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(rsa.decrypt(fp.read(), privatekey).decode())</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","text":"RSA256得到为RSA密钥文件以及密文，利用openssl库，打开密钥文件，得到N和公钥， [Figure] ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"你猜猜","slug":"yougues","date":"2021-01-24T02:04:50.624Z","updated":"2021-01-24T02:24:20.733Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/yougues.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210124100252256.png#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4930&page=1\">你猜猜</a><br>得到txt文件后，发现文本内容为504B开头，猜测为zip文件格式，于是用python将其转化为zip文件后，发<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210124100252256.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>现可以可以正常打开，内含有flag.txt文件。</p>\n<p>但是需要密码才能打开，暴力破解得到得到密码为123456</p>\n<p>脚本如下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> struct</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># guess.txt即为输入文件，test.zip即为输出文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">file = <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;gess.txt&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;r&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">ss = file.read()</span><br><span class=\"line\">f = <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;test.zip&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;wb&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">i = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> i &lt; <span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(ss):</span><br><span class=\"line\"> s = ss[i:i+<span class=\"number\">2</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"> temp = <span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(s, <span class=\"number\">16</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> f.write(struct.pack(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;B&#x27;</span>, temp))</span><br><span class=\"line\"> i += <span class=\"number\">2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">file.close()</span><br><span class=\"line\">f.close()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> zipfile</span><br><span class=\"line\">zFile = zipfile.ZipFile(<span class=\"string\">&quot;test.zip&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">pwdlists=<span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">r&#x27;C:\\Users\\13762\\Desktop\\password.txt&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> line <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> pwdlists.readlines():</span><br><span class=\"line\">    password=line.strip(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;\\n&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">#print(1,end=&#x27;&#x27;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">try</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">        zFile.extractall(path=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;flag&#x27;</span>,pwd=password)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;password is:&quot;</span>+password)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">except</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(password)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">pass</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","text":"你猜猜<br>得到txt文件后，发现文本内容为504B开头，猜测为zip文件格式，于是用python将其转化为zip文件后，发 [Figure] ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"re1-100","slug":"re1-100 WP","date":"2021-01-17T14:14:44.270Z","updated":"2021-01-17T14:27:56.877Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/re1-100 WP.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117221031459.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=reverse&number=4&grade=1&id=4720&page=2\">re1-100</a><br>1.附件为pe文件，使用ida64打开文件，找到main函数，<br>发现对输入字符串，进行比较后，与一段给定字符串，进行比较是否相等，<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117221031459.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>2.再confuseKey函数中，对于字符串进行了操作之后，再进行比较，打开该函数，进行分析可以发现。<br>函数功能为将括号内部分分为4组，然后交换顺序，得到新的字符串，进行输出<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117221324774.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>3.交换后结果为</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> {53fc275d81053ed5be8cdaf29f59034938ae4efd}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>注意提交是要去掉{}<br><del>捂脸</del> </p>\n","text":"re1-100<br>1.附件为pe文件，使用ida64打开文件，找到main函数，<br>发现对输入字符串，进行比较后，与一段给定字符串，进行比较是否相等，<br> [Figure] 捂脸 ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Windows_Reverse1","slug":"Windows_Reverse1 WP","date":"2021-01-17T14:02:36.210Z","updated":"2021-01-17T14:28:09.124Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows_Reverse1 WP.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117215443379.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=reverse&number=4&grade=1&id=5514&page=2\">Windows_Reverse1</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>检测是否有壳<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117215443379.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></li>\n</ol>\n<p>发现有upx壳，于是使用upx -d进行脱壳，并对脱壳后的程序使用ida分析</p>\n<p>2.观察main函数后，发现经过sub_40100（）函数后，得到了字符串DDCTF{reverseME}，<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117215938470.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>3.sub401000后发现，分析为对字符串查询为在ox402ff8后的地址，将其作为字典取出，注意前后存在的多余空格字节，就可以得到flag：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ZZ[JX#,9(9,+9QY!</p>\n</blockquote>\n","text":"Windows_Reverse1检测是否有壳<br> [Figure] 3.sub401000后发现，分析为对字符串查询为在ox402ff8后的地址，将其作为字典取出，注意前后存在的多余空格字节，就可以得到flag：ZZ[JX#,9(9,+9QY!","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Newbie_calculations","slug":"XCTFNewbie_calculations","date":"2021-01-09T06:10:47.440Z","updated":"2021-01-09T06:20:32.628Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/XCTFNewbie_calculations.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210109140716669.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=reverse&number=4&grade=1&id=4973&page=2\">Newbie_calculations</a></p>\n<p>得到的32位exe文件，使用ida分析，发现程序一直再调用三个程序，但是运行程序却没有结果</p>\n<p>于是打开三个程序进行分析，发现程序依次进行的对应的为加减乘三种运算，但是在进行运算时，程序时进行的+1的操作，借助有符号数的边界进行。</p>\n<p>经过适当的修改之后，就可以得到main（）的功能<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210109140716669.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>其中v120为一个被初始化为1 的数组，也是最后的结果数组，分析整个程序之后，就可以得到flag</p>\n","text":"Newbie_calculations得到的32位exe文件，使用ida分析，发现程序一直再调用三个程序，但是运行程序却没有结果于是打开三个程序进行分析，发现程序依次进行的对应的为加减乘三种运算，但是在进行运算时，程序时进行的+1的操作，借助有符号数的边界进行。经过适当的修改之后","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"oldDriver","slug":"XCTFoldDriver","date":"2021-01-09T03:49:00.549Z","updated":"2021-01-09T06:20:23.762Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/XCTFoldDriver.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4672&page=1\">oldDriver</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[{“c”: 7366067574741171461722065133242916080495505913663250330082747465383676893970411476550748394841437418105312353971095003424322679616940371123028982189502042, “e”: 10, “n”: 2516250705