486615661699080998502439901585573950889047918537906687840725005496238621&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">M = n1*n2*n3*n4*n5*n6*n7*n8*n9*n0</span><br><span class=\"line\">m1 = M//n1</span><br><span class=\"line\">m2 = M//n2</span><br><span class=\"line\">m3 = M//n3</span><br><span class=\"line\">m4 = M//n4</span><br><span class=\"line\">m5 = M//n5</span><br><span class=\"line\">m6 = M//n6</span><br><span class=\"line\">m7 = M//n7</span><br><span class=\"line\">m8 = M//n8</span><br><span class=\"line\">m9 = M//n9</span><br><span class=\"line\">m0 = M//n0</span><br><span class=\"line\">t1 = c1 * (m1) * gmpy2.invert(m1, n1)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t2 = c2 * (m2) * gmpy2.invert(m2, n2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t3 = c3 * (m3) * gmpy2.invert(m3, n3)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t4 = c4 * (m4) * gmpy2.invert(m4, n4)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t5 = c5 * (m5) * gmpy2.invert(m5, n5)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t6 = c6 * (m6) * gmpy2.invert(m6, n6)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t7 = c7 * (m7) * gmpy2.invert(m7, n7)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t8 = c8 * (m8) * gmpy2.invert(m8, n8)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t9 = c9 * (m9) * gmpy2.invert(m9, n9)</span><br><span class=\"line\">t0 = c0 * (m0) * gmpy2.invert(m0, n0)</span><br><span class=\"line\">e=<span class=\"number\">10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">x = (t1+t2+t3+t4+t5+t6+t7+t8+t9+t0) % M <span class=\"comment\"># chinese reminder theorem m, exact =</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">m=gmpy2.iroot(x,e) <span class=\"comment\"># recover m if exact: print</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(m)</span><br><span class=\"line\">a,b=m</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(libnum.n2s(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(a)))</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","text":"oldDriver[{“c”: 7366067574741171461722065133242916080495505913663250330082747465383676893970411476550748394841437418105312353971095003424322","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"如来十三掌","slug":"XCTF-ro13","date":"2021-01-09T03:11:45.301Z","updated":"2021-01-09T06:20:16.585Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/XCTF-ro13.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=misc&number=1&grade=0&id=5106&page=1\">如来十三掌</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>夜哆悉諳多苦奢陀奢諦冥神哆盧穆皤三侄三即諸諳即冥迦冥隸數顛耶迦奢若吉怯陀諳怖奢智侄諸若奢數菩奢集遠俱老竟寫明奢若梵等盧皤豆蒙密離怯婆皤礙他哆提哆多缽以南哆心曰姪罰蒙呐神。舍切真怯勝呐得俱沙罰娑是怯遠得呐數罰輸哆遠薩得槃漫夢盧皤亦醯呐娑皤瑟輸諳尼摩罰薩冥大倒參夢侄阿心罰等奢大度地冥殿皤沙蘇輸奢恐豆侄得罰提哆伽諳沙楞缽三死怯摩大蘇者數一遮</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>得到是佛的禅语（凡人看不懂.jpg）<br><del>所以需要有人帮我们找到理解禅意的方法</del><br>于是找的解码网站<br><a href=\"http://www.keyfc.net/bbs/tools/tudoucode.aspx\">与佛论禅</a><br>解码之后得到一串字符</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>MzkuM3gvMUAwnzuvn3cgozMlMTuvqzAenJchMUAeqzWenzEmLJW9</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>然后根据WP（捂脸）可以知道使用了ro13这种加密方法，于是进行<a href=\"http://www.rot13.de/index.php\">解码</a>，</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ZmxhZ3tiZHNjamhia3ptbmZyZGhidmNraWpuZHNrdmJramRzYWJ9</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>再进行base64解码就能得到flag</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>flag{bdscjhbkzmnfrdhbvckijndskvbkjdsab}</p>\n</blockquote>\n","text":"如来十三掌夜哆悉諳多苦奢陀奢諦冥神哆盧穆皤三侄三即諸諳即冥迦冥隸數顛耶迦奢若吉怯陀諳怖奢智侄諸若奢數菩奢集遠俱老竟寫明奢若梵等盧皤豆蒙密離怯婆皤礙他哆提哆多缽以南哆心曰姪罰蒙呐神。舍切真怯勝呐得俱沙罰娑是怯遠得呐數罰輸哆遠薩得槃漫夢盧皤亦醯呐娑皤瑟輸諳尼摩罰薩冥大倒參夢侄阿心罰等","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"flag_in_your_hand","slug":"flag_in_your_hand1","date":"2020-12-28T12:37:55.565Z","updated":"2021-01-09T01:56:03.585Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/flag_in_your_hand1.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228195218456.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4869&page=1\">flag_in_your_hand</a><br>本题的附加为一个html网页和对于的js源码，直接用浏览器打开页面，<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228195218456.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>使用浏览器的调试功能，可以观察具体的运行过程，略过复杂度的转换过程，可以发现输入的字符串都会经过ck函数<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228195158430.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>进行判断，如果为判断结果为真，就可以得到flag，简单计算得到对应的字符串，输入得到最后的flag<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201228195419888.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>crypto类型的题目可能会涉及多方面知识，以后应该学习各个方向的知识，才能更好的解决问题</p>\n</blockquote>\n","text":"flag_in_your_hand<br>本题的附加为一个html网页和对于的js源码，直接用浏览器打开页面，<br> [Figure] crypto类型的题目可能会涉及多方面知识，以后应该学习各个方向的知识，才能更好的解决问题","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"告诉你个秘密","slug":"keyboard","date":"2020-12-28T12:37:30.657Z","updated":"2021-01-09T01:56:11.101Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/keyboard.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4929&page=1\">告诉你个秘密</a></p>\n<p>附件为一个txt文件，里面内容只有2行</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>636A56355279427363446C4A49454A7154534230526D6843<br>56445A31614342354E326C4B4946467A5769426961453067</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>观察发现里面所有的字符，都不大于F，所以可以首先尝试将其按照ascii的十六进制解码得到另一串字符串</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>cjV5RyBscDlJIEJqTSB0RmhCVDZ1aCB5N2lKIFFzWiBiaE0g</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>字符串中出现了字母数字组合，且没有不可见字母，所以使用base64解码</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>r5yG lp9I BjM tFhBT6uh y7iJ QsZ bhM </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>有明显的分组特征，经过观察发现其在键盘上的位置刚好可以围住一些字母，按照这种规则走下去，可以得到一个意义的字符串，也就是flag</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>TONGYUAN</p>\n</blockquote>\n","text":"告诉你个秘密附件为一个txt文件，里面内容只有2行636A56355279427363446C4A49454A7154534230526D6843<br>56445A31614342354E326C4B4946467A5769426961453067观察发现里面所有的字符，都不大","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]}]}